164
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:31,360
Did you get injured?

165
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:34,480
No, no.

166
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:49,710
Why is everyone here?

167
00:17:51,170 --> 00:17:53,540
What happened to me?

168
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:56,820
It was tough for you to guard the city.

169
00:17:56,820 --> 00:18:01,540
You were so stressed out that once you relaxed, your body couldn't take it anymore.

170
00:18:01,540 --> 00:18:05,750
Sister Jun, you finally woke up.

171
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:14,780
Your Highness, you were very brave at the gate tower.

172
00:18:14,780 --> 00:18:17,150
Because you encouraged me.

173
00:18:17,150 --> 00:18:21,190
Thank you, Sister Jun, for protecting me at the gate tower.

174
00:18:23,010 --> 00:18:25,460
You're welcome, Your Highness.

175
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:35,430
Physician Jun, you've done so much.

176
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:38,870
Why did you let His Majesty take all the credit?

177
00:18:44,740 --> 00:18:49,780
If I hadn't done it, he wouldn't come back.

178
00:18:53,290 --> 00:18:58,420
We should put an end to some things.

179
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:06,630
But everyone in the city has seen Jiurong.

180
00:19:06,630 --> 00:19:11,860
I don't know what will happen when His Majesty comes back.

181
00:19:29,850 --> 00:19:34,620
We could guard the capital because of your effort.

182
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:39,340
On behalf of the Chu family, I'd like to thank you.

183
00:20:03,410 --> 00:20:08,540
I'm also happy to be able to protect our home.

184
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:21,840
Lady Flower, Lady Grass,

185
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:26,560
Lady Rock, Lady Soil.

186
00:20:27,930 --> 00:20:31,380
Which lady comes? Which lady goes?

187
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:33,780
Lady Flower, Lady Grass,

188
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:37,560
Lady Rock, Lady Soil. Which lady comes?

189
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:39,970
Jiuling, what are you doing?

190
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:44,200
- Sister, I'm looking for Lady Bug. Do you know what Lady Bug is?
- So dirty.

191
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,660
Here.

192
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:50,870
As a princess, you should behave like a princess.

193
00:20:50,870 --> 00:20:54,330
See how dirty you are? Father will scold you if he sees it.

194
00:20:54,330 --> 00:20:57,960
If I have to behave well every day, it'll be boring.

195
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:04,840
As a descendant of the imperial family, this is a rule you should follow.

196
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:07,150
Sister, I don't want to follow rules.

197
00:21:07,150 --> 00:21:09,280
I want to go out for fun.

198
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:20,490
Jiuling, what did you say just now?

199
00:21:20,490 --> 00:21:22,160
It sounded nice.

200
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:25,800
Why don't you say it to me again?

201
00:21:25,800 --> 00:21:27,480
Sure.

202
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,990
Lady Flower, Lady Grass...

203
00:21:29,990 --> 00:21:33,490
Lady Rock, Lady Soil.

204
00:21:33,490 --> 00:21:36,300
Which lady comes? Which lady goes?

205
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:38,930
Which lady comes?

206
00:21:39,820 --> 00:21:42,420
Which lady goes?

207
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:46,620
Lady Red, Lady White, Lady Yellow.

208
00:21:47,410 --> 00:21:50,540
Sister, it's Lady Bug.

209
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:53,320
Jiuling, what's that?

210
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:55,590
It's Lady Bug, sister. Look.

211
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:57,680
- Jiuling, don't come to me.
- Sister. Sister, look!

212
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,240
Jiuling, don't come to me!

213
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:02,170
- Sister, don't be afraid!
- I don't like bugs.

214
00:22:04,660 --> 00:22:06,460
Don't be afraid!

215
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:21,500
You are Ling'er?

216
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:27,000
Sister.

217
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:31,100
Since that time you reprimanded me,

218
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:36,600
I did not play with Lady Bug ever again.

219
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:38,200
But...

220
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:42,100
But your appearance and voice, how did it become like this now?

221
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:45,130
It's a long story.

222
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:51,000
After all, if not for Master Jin and his daughter's help,

223
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:55,060
I probably wouldn't have been able to see you guys in this lifetime.

224
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,800
Rong'er, come here.

225
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:06,600
Second Older Sister, you came back.

226
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,380
Rong'er.

227
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:17,200
You finally came back.

228
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:20,300
Second Older Sister, is it really you?

229
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:24,900
Yes, it's me.

230
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,600
I came back.

231
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:30,600
Second Sister.

232
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:40,600
Rong'er, don't cry. Shouldn't we be smiling?

233
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:43,200
You say, you are still alive.

234
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:46,100
Why didn't you come forward earlier?

235
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:48,800
You married Lu Yunqi, it already put you in a tough situation.

236
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:52,000
How could I make it even worse for you?

237
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,700
Besides,

238
00:23:54,710 --> 00:23:59,000
I already made Lu Yunqi suspect me because of the name Jiuling.

239
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,500
He has been watching me secretly.

240
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:04,800
So I couldn't show any flaws.

241
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:07,200
I actually was trying to find a chance

242
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:10,200
to tell you guys everything.

243
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:16,880
You suffered so much by yourself.

244
00:24:17,650 --> 00:24:21,010
I feel so bad as an older sister.

245
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:24,200
So sorry.

246
00:24:25,800 --> 00:24:29,000
We are a family,

247
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:32,100
so from now on,

248
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:36,200
don't take on so much by yourself.

249
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:39,800
Everything, we will deal with it together.

250
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:42,300
All right?

251
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:48,800
Yes, Older sister.

252
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:18,580
Jiuling, you will go to the palace tomorrow. Are you nervous?

253
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,700
I waited for so long,

254
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:24,000
finally waiting for this day for the truth to be revealed.

255
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:28,300
God is fair, you will get what you wish for.

256
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,400
Chengyu came back with me,

257
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:44,700
but I was afraid he would get noticed going in and out of Jiuling Hall.

